                        <h3><a href="#">Denominator Inclusions/Exclusions</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p><strong>Inclusions</strong><br/>
Number of hospitalized patients who received an initial* consult visit by specialty palliative care between 24 and 72 hours prior to the time of item administration </p>
<p class="Note">*<em>Initial</em> refers to the first palliative care consult during this admission.</p>
<p><strong>Exclusions</strong><br/>
Unspecified</p></div></p>
                        <h3><a href="#">Exclusions/Exceptions</a></h3>
                    <p>Does not apply to this measure</p>
