    <li><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Option B</span></strong> ("At or Near Goal"): Number of respondents who endorse either "Completely" or "Quite a Bit" </li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Exclusions</strong><br/>
Unspecified</p></div></p>
